座，您无需在相当长的时间内清空底座，因为它声称可以使用长达 45 天。虽然我们没有尝试这个确切的模型，但我们发现 Shark 的机器人真空吸尘器设置起来很简单，并且有一个特别易于使用的配套应用程序。 Shark 的地图功能通常很准确，从长远来看，这里的无袋底座应该可以为您节省金钱，因为购买特定于设备的袋子可能会很昂贵。</p><h2>三星 Galaxy Watch 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="82b39bb57d2e41dab1c787229046a5f2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:68;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjVUQjNRP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE0YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzkxN2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWiQntQfuL-DpTNEDx9m5QPh_cN-L6WPbhTNq0SxIGRo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J5TB3Q">三星 Galaxy Watch 5</a> 40 毫米型号降至 199 美元， <a data-i13n="cpos:69;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjRXNVRUP3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAU1TmQmGcWLZhjXtQLGpqR2ggaG5X4r_eZuqNKt3fF-7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J4W5TT%3Fth%3D1">44 毫米型号</a>降至 229 美元。去年我们给 Galaxy Watch 5 <a data-i13n="cpos:70;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-5-pro-review-battery-life-specs-durability-180052187.html">的评分为 85 分</a>，目前它是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:71;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">智能手表购买